<h3>NIGHT TIME</h3>

<p>You are <span class="player-name"><%= @player.display_name %></span>, a <%= Player::ROLES[@player.role] %></p>

<% if @eliminated_player %>
  <p>The villagers voted to eliminated <span class="player-name"><%= @eliminated_player.display_name %></span>. This player was a <%= Player::ROLES[@eliminated_player.role] %></p>
<% end %>

<% if @player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:VILLAGER] %>
  <p>Your goal as a villager is to eliminate all of the mafiosi.</p>

  <p>During the night you have no actions to take. Day will begin when the following nighttime actions have completed:</p>
<% end %>

<% if @player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:MAFIOSO] %>
  <p>Your goal as a mafioso is to eliminate all of the villagers. You will win if the number of villagers equals the number of mafiosi.</p>

  <p>This game's mafiosi are:</p>
  <%= render "noninteractive_player_list", player_list: @mafiosi %>

  <p>During the night you and the other mafiosi will choose a villager to attack. This decision must be unanimous. If it is not unanimous no one will be attacked.</p>
<% end %>

<% if @player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:DETECTIVE] %>
  <p>Your goal as a detective is to eliminate all of the mafiosi.</p>

  <p>During the night you have may choose a villager to visit. If that villager is a Mafioso they will be eliminated. <% if @game.remaining_detective_investigations > 0 %>You may do this <b><%= @game.remaining_detective_investigations %></b> more times. <% end %></p>

  <% if @game.remaining_detective_investigations > 0 %>
    <% if @player_action and @player_action.target_id == @player.id %>
      <p>You have chosen not to do an investigation tonight. You can change your mind by choosing someone to visit below.</p>
    <% else %>
      <%= form_with model: @player_action, id: "player_actions#{@player.id}" do |form| %>
        <%= form.hidden_field :player_id, value: @player.id %>
        <%= form.hidden_field :round_id, value: @current_round.id %>
        <%= form.hidden_field :target_id, value: @player.id %>
        <%= form.submit  "Investigate no one tonight" %>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  <% else %>
    <p>You have used all your investigations for this game.</p>
  <% end %>
<% end %>

<% if @player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:DOCTOR] %>
  <p>Your goal as a doctor is to eliminate all of the mafiosi.</p>

  <p>During the night you have must choose a villager to visit. If that villager is attacked you will prevent that villager from dying.</p>
<% end %>

<%= render "night_actions_explainer", use_detective: @game.use_detective, use_doctor: @game.use_doctor %>

<% if @player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:MAFIOSO] %>
  <p>Choose your target</p>
  <%= render "interactive_player_list",
             player_list: @non_mafiosi,
             current_player_action: @player_action,
             current_round: @current_round,
             current_player: @player,
             show_target_of: "ROLE",
             show_target_of_role: [PLAYER_ROLE[:MAFIOSO]] %>
<% elsif (@player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:DETECTIVE] and @game.remaining_detective_investigations > 0) or @player.role == PLAYER_ROLE[:DOCTOR] %>
  <p>Choose a player to visit:</p>
  <%= render "interactive_player_list",
             ignore_current_player: true,
             player_list: @game.player.filter { |player| player.alive == true },
             current_player_action: @player_action,
             current_round: @current_round,
             current_player: @player,
             show_target_of: "NONE" %>
<% end %>